Have fun!

Current Version: 4

Screens are from V3

V1->V2 changes:

-Less glass: More fair and glass is now green.
-New Bullettime mode when you break the box on map.
-Some repairs.


V2->V3 changes:

-Added some crates to upper floor.
-Deleted bullettime mode it was bit stupid because it activates cheats and you can do mat_wireframe then.

V3->V4 changes:

-Optimized
-Some fixes.
-Some Textures changed and some new lights.
-Secret. (Tip: Press 4 buttons and break 2 things and it will trigger.)

V4->V5 changes:

-Deleted dumb secret
-Tower is now at middle and no roof at middle anymore
-Some texture placements fixed
-Made vent different
